---
import ReferenciasPautas from "./ReferenciasPautas.astro";
---

<div id="info-orales-combinados" class="info-content hidden rounded-t-3xl">
  <div class="md:hidden bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-6">
    <div
      class="bg-purple-abbott text-white p-4 text-center font-bold uppercase tracking-wide"
    >
      Anticonceptivos Orales Combinados
    </div>

    <div class="p-4 border-b border-gray-100">
      <span class="block text-black font-bold uppercase text-xs mb-1"
        >Cómo actúan</span
      >
      <p>Inhiben la ovulación</p>
    </div>

    <div class="p-4 border-b border-gray-100">
      <span class="block text-black font-bold uppercase text-xs mb-2"
        >Efectividad (Índice de Pearl)</span
      >
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <div class="flex-1 p-3 rounded text-center">
          <span class="block text-2xl font-extrabold text-black">0,3</span>
          <span class="block text-xs font-bold text-purple-abbott">99.7% de efectividad</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-600">Uso Correcto*</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 p-3 rounded text-center">
          <span class="block text-2xl font-extrabold text-black">7</span>
          <span class="block text-xs font-bold text-purple-abbott">93% de efectividad</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-600">Uso Típico*</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="p-4 border-b border-gray-100">
      <span class="block text-black font-bold uppercase text-xs mb-1"
        >Cuándo Iniciar</span
      >
      <p>
        En cualquier momento del mes.<br /><span class="text-xs text-gray-500"
          >>5 días desde el inicio de la menstruación, necesita método de
          respaldo por 7 días.</span
        >
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="p-4">
      <span class="block text-black font-bold uppercase text-xs mb-1"
        >Modo de Uso</span
      >
      <p class="mb-2">Una píldora diaria a la misma hora.</p>
      <div class="text-xs text-gray-600 space-y-1">
        <p>
          • <strong>21 píldoras:</strong> descansa 7 días antes de iniciar el nuevo
          envase.
        </p>
        <p>• <strong>28 píldoras:</strong> uso continuo.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="overflow-x-auto px-2 md:px-0 rounded-t-3xl md:border md:border-purple-abbott"
  >
    <table
      class="w-full border-collapse bg-white md:rounded-none rounded-lg overflow-hidden"
    >
      <thead class="hidden md:table-header-group text-white">
        <tr>
          <th
            colspan="7"
            class="bg-purple-abbott p-4 text-xl uppercase border-b-2 border-white"
          >
            Anticonceptivos Orales Combinados (AOC)
          </th>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-purple-abbott/70 text-xs uppercase">
          <th
            rowspan="2"
            class="border border-white p-2 border-b-purple-abbott border-l-purple-abbott"
            >Cómo actúan</th
          >
          <th colspan="2" class="border border-white p-2"
            >Efectividad<sup>1</sup></th
          >
          <th rowspan="2" class="border border-white p-2 border-b-purple-abbott"
            >Cuándo iniciar</th
          >
          <th
            rowspan="2"
            class="border border-white p-2 border-b-purple-abbott w-1/6"
            >Modo / Frecuencia</th
          >
          <th
            rowspan="2"
            class="border border-white p-2 border-b-purple-abbott w-1/6"
            >Opciones</th
          >
          <th
            rowspan="2"
            class="border border-white p-2 border-b-purple-abbott w-1/4"
            >Beneficios Adicionales</th
          >
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-purple-abbott/70 text-xs uppercase">
          <th class="border border-white p-2 border-b-purple-abbott"
            >Uso Correcto*</th
          >
          <th class="border border-white p-2 border-b-purple-abbott"
            >Uso Típico*</th
          >
        </tr>
      </thead>

      <tbody class="block md:table-row-group">
        <tr
          class="flex flex-col md:table-row mb-4 md:mb-0 bg-white md:bg-transparent shadow md:shadow-none border border-purple-abbott md:border-none rounded-lg md:rounded-none overflow-hidden mt-1"
        >
          <td
            rowspan="13"
            class="hidden md:table-cell bg-purple-abbott/70 text-white font-bold text-center border border-purple-abbott p-3 text-lg align-middle"
          >
            Inhiben la ovulación
          </td>
          <td
            rowspan="13"
            class="hidden md:table-cell text-center border border-purple-abbott p-3 font-extrabold text-xl align-middle"
            >0,3<span class="block text-xs font-bold text-purple-abbott">99,9% de efectividad</span></td
          >
          <td
            rowspan="13"
            class="hidden md:table-cell text-center border border-purple-abbott p-3 font-extrabold text-xl align-middle"
            >7<span class="block text-xs font-bold text-purple-abbott">93% de efectividad</span></td
          >
          <td
            rowspan="13"
            class="hidden md:table-cell border border-purple-abbott p-4 align-middle"
          >
            <strong>En cualquier momento del mes:</strong><br /><br />
            <span class="text-xs"
              >>5 días desde el inicio de la menstruación, necesita método de
              respaldo por 7 días.</span
            >
          </td>
          <td
            rowspan="13"
            class="hidden md:table-cell border border-purple-abbott p-4 align-middle"
          >
            <strong>Una píldora diaria a la misma hora.</strong><br /><br />
            <span class="text-xs block mb-2"
              ><strong>21 píldoras:</strong> descansa 7 días antes de iniciar el nuevo
              envase.</span
            >
            <span class="text-xs block"
              ><strong>28 píldoras:</strong> no descansa entre un envase y otro.</span
            >
          </td>

          <td
            class="block md:table-cell p-4 md:text-black border border-purple-abbott text-center font-bold md:align-middle"
          >
            <span class="text-lg md:text-base">Bellanew</span>
            <span
              class="block text-xs font-normal text-purple-abbott/80 md:text-gray-500 mt-1"
              >1,5mg Estradiol hemidrato / 2mg Dienogest</span
            >
          </td>
          <td
            class="block md:table-cell p-4 border border-purple-abbott align-middle"
          >
            <span
              class="md:hidden text-black font-bold text-xs uppercase mb-2 block"
              >Beneficios:</span
            >
            <strong class="text-xs md:text-sm"
              >Estrógeno bioidéntico al natural:</strong
            >
            <ul class="list-disc marker:text-[10px] text-xs md:text-sm">
              <li>Menor riesgo de eventos adversos.<sup>2</sup></li>
              <li>Menor impacto metabólico.<sup>2</sup></li>
              <li>
                Potente actividad antiandrogénica (mejoría de acné, hirsutismo,
                piel y cabello grasos).<sup>3</sup>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr
          class="flex flex-col md:table-row mb-4 md:mb-0 bg-white md:bg-transparent shadow md:shadow-none border border-purple-abbott md:border-none rounded-lg md:rounded-none overflow-hidden"
        >
          <td
            class="block md:table-cell p-4 md: text-black border border-purple-abbott text-center font-bold md:align-middle"
          >
            <span class="text-lg md:text-base">Bellaface</span>
            <span
              class="block text-xs font-normal text-purple-abbott/80 md:text-gray-500 mt-1"
              >2mg Dienogest /0,03mg Etinilestradiol</span
            >
          </td>
          <td
            class="block md:table-cell p-4 border border-purple-abbott align-middle"
          >
            <span
              class="md:hidden text-black font-bold text-xs uppercase mb-2 block"
              >Beneficios:</span
            >
            <ul class="list-disc marker:text-[10px] text-xs md:text-sm">
              <li>Actividad antiandrogénica.<sup>3</sup></li>
              <li>
                Reducción de la intensidad y duración del sangrado menstrual.<sup
                  >4</sup>
              </li>
              <li>Mejoría dismenorrea.<sup>5</sup></li>
            </ul>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr
          class="flex flex-col md:table-row mb-4 md:mb-0 bg-white md:bg-transparent shadow md:shadow-none border border-purple-abbott md:border-none rounded-lg md:rounded-none overflow-hidden"
        >
          <td
            class="block md:table-cell p-4 md: text-black border border-purple-abbott text-center font-bold md:align-middle"
          >
            <span class="text-lg md:text-base">Bellaface suave</span>
            <span
              class="block text-xs font-normal text-purple-abbott/80 md:text-gray-500 mt-1"
              >2mg Dienogest /20mg Etilestradiol</span
            >
          </td>
          <td
            class="block md:table-cell p-4 border border-purple-abbott align-middle"
          >
            <span
              class="md:hidden text-black font-bold text-xs uppercase mb-2 block"
              >Beneficios:</span
            >
            <ul class="list-disc marker:text-[10px] text-xs md:text-sm">
              <li>
                Actividad antiandrogénica con menos carga hormonal.<sup>6</sup>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr
          class="flex flex-col md:table-row mb-4 md:mb-0 bg-white md:bg-transparent shadow md:shadow-none border border-purple-abbott md:border-none rounded-lg md:rounded-none overflow-hidden"
        >
          <td
            class="block md:table-cell p-4 md:text-black border border-purple-abbott text-center font-bold md:align-middle"
          >
            <span class="text-lg md:text-base">Femelle</span>
            <span
              class="block text-xs font-normal text-purple-abbott/80 md:text-gray-500 mt-1"
              >Drospirenona 3mg/etinilestradiol 0,02 mg</span
            >
          </td>
          <td
            class="block md:table-cell p-4 border border-purple-abbott align-middle"
          >
            <span
              class="md:hidden text-black font-bold text-xs uppercase mb-2 block"
              >Beneficios:</span
            >
            <ul class="list-disc marker:text-[10px] text-xs md:text-sm">
              <li>
                Mejoría de los síntomas del síndrome disfórico premenstrual
                (SDPM).<sup>7</sup>
              </li>
              <li>Mejoría de la dismenorrea.<sup>7</sup></li>
              <li>Actividad antiandrogénica.<sup>7</sup></li>
              <li>Actividad antimineralocorticoide.<sup>5</sup></li>
            </ul>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr
          class="flex flex-col md:table-row mb-4 md:mb-0 bg-white md:bg-transparent shadow md:shadow-none border border-purple-abbott md:border-none rounded-lg md:rounded-none overflow-hidden"
        >
          <td
            class="block md:table-cell p-4 md:text-black border border-purple-abbott text-center font-bold md:align-middle"
          >
            <span class="text-lg md:text-base">Yax</span>
            <span
              class="block text-xs font-normal text-purple-abbott/80 md:text-gray-500 mt-1"
              >Drospirenona 3,0mg / Etinilestradiol 0,003mg</span
            >
          </td>
          <td
            class="block md:table-cell p-4 border border-purple-abbott align-middle"
          >
            <span
              class="md:hidden text-black font-bold text-xs uppercase mb-2 block"
              >Beneficios:</span
            >
            <strong class="text-xs md:text-sm"
              >Propiedades antimineralocorticoides:</strong
            >
            <ul class="list-disc marker:text-[10px] text-xs md:text-sm">
              <li>Sin impacto sobre el peso corporal.<sup>5</sup></li>
              <li>Mejoría de la dismenorrea.<sup>7</sup></li>
            </ul>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr
          class="flex flex-col md:table-row mb-4 md:mb-0 bg-white md:bg-transparent shadow md:shadow-none border border-purple-abbott md:border-none rounded-lg md:rounded-none overflow-hidden"
        >
          <td
            class="block md:table-cell p-4 text-black border border-purple-abbott text-center font-bold md:align-middle"
          >
            <span class="text-lg md:text-base">Yaxibelle</span>
            <span
              class="block text-xs font-normal text-purple-abbott/80 md:text-gray-500 mt-1"
              >Drospirenona 3,0mg/Etinilestradiol 0,002mg</span
            >
          </td>
          <td
            class="block md:table-cell p-4 border border-purple-abbott align-middle"
          >
            <span
              class="md:hidden text-black font-bold text-xs uppercase mb-2 block"
              >Beneficios:</span
            >
            <ul class="list-disc marker:text-[10px] text-xs md:text-sm">
              <li>
                Mejoría de los síntomas del síndrome disfórico premenstrual
                (SDPM).<sup>7</sup>
              </li>
              <li>Mejoría de la dismenorrea.<sup>7</sup></li>
              <li>Actividad antiandrogénica.<sup>7</sup></li>
              <li>Actividad antimineralocorticoide.<sup>5</sup></li>
            </ul>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr
          class="flex flex-col md:table-row mb-4 md:mb-0 bg-white md:bg-transparent shadow md:shadow-none border border-purple-abbott md:border-none rounded-lg md:rounded-none overflow-hidden"
        >
          <td
            class="block md:table-cell p-4 md: text-black border border-purple-abbott text-center font-bold md:align-middle"
          >
            <span class="text-lg md:text-base">Gynorelle</span>
            <span
              class="block text-xs font-normal text-purple-abbott/80 md:text-gray-500 mt-1"
              >Clormadinona/ Acetato 2mg / Etinilestradiol 0,02 mg</span
            >
          </td>
          <td
            class="block md:table-cell p-4 border border-purple-abbott align-middle"
          >
            <span
              class="md:hidden text-black font-bold text-xs uppercase mb-2 block"
              >Beneficios:</span
            >
            <ul class="list-disc marker:text-[10px] text-xs md:text-sm">
              <li>
                Efecto neuroendocrino que promueve sensación de bienestar.<sup
                  >8</sup>
              </li>
              <li>
                Mejoría del estado de ánimo, reducción de molestias emocionales
                y físicas.<sub>8</sub>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr
          class="flex flex-col md:table-row mb-4 md:mb-0 bg-white md:bg-transparent shadow md:shadow-none border border-purple-abbott md:border-none rounded-lg md:rounded-none overflow-hidden"
        >
          <td
            class="block md:table-cell p-4 md: text-black border border-purple-abbott text-center font-bold md:align-middle"
          >
            <span class="text-lg md:text-base">Gynorelle 30</span>
            <span
              class="block text-xs font-normal text-purple-abbott/80 md:text-gray-500 mt-1"
              >Clormadinona Acetato 2mg / Etinilestradiol 0,03 mg</span
            >
          </td>
          <td
            class="block md:table-cell p-4 border border-purple-abbott align-middle"
          >
            <span
              class="md:hidden text-black font-bold text-xs uppercase mb-2 block"
              >Beneficios:</span
            >
            <ul class="list-disc marker:text-[10px] text-xs md:text-sm">
              <li>
                Efecto neuroendocrino que promueve sensación de bienestar.<sup
                  >8</sup>
              </li>
              <li>
                Mejoría del estado de ánimo, reducción de molestias emocionales
                y físicas.<sup>8</sup>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr
          class="flex flex-col md:table-row mb-4 md:mb-0 bg-white md:bg-transparent shadow md:shadow-none border border-purple-abbott md:border-none rounded-lg md:rounded-none overflow-hidden"
        >
          <td
            class="block md:table-cell p-4 md:text-black border border-purple-abbott text-center font-bold md:align-middle"
          >
            <span class="text-lg md:text-base">Sinovul</span>
            <span
              class="block text-xs font-normal text-purple-abbott/80 md:text-gray-500 mt-1"
              >levonorgestrel 0,15mg /etinilestradiol0,03mg</span
            >
          </td>
          <td
            class="block md:table-cell p-4 border border-purple-abbott align-middle"
          >
            <span
              class="md:hidden text-black font-bold text-xs uppercase mb-2 block"
              >Beneficios:</span
            >
            <ul class="list-disc marker:text-[10px] text-xs md:text-sm">
              <li>Regulación del ciclo.<sup>5</sup></li>
            </ul>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  <p class="mt-4 ml-4">
    *Se recomienda el uso simultáneo de preservativo para evitar el contagio de
    ITS. <sup>1</sup>
  </p>
  <div class="mt-4 p-4 text-xs space-y-1">
    <div class="mt-2">
      <ReferenciasPautas />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
